('bhote', 'Bhote', 'Tibeto-Burman language of Bhote communities in high Himalayan areas.', 'SINO_TIBETAN', 'VULNERABLE', 15000, 'Tibetan', 'Devanagari', 'Standard Bhote', false, false, 'HIMALAYAN', 'Bagmati', 'Related to Tibetan. Bhote communities are traditionally pastoral and trade-oriented.', 'Connected to Tibetan Buddhist culture and high-altitude pastoral life.', NULL, 'Declining due to modernization and low population.', NOW()),

